OL,3,CDisused coal tips safety bill becomes
OL,4,Claw in Wales
OL,6,FFirst Minister Eluned Morgan has
OL,7,Fofficially sealed the Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment's coal tip safety bill in a
OL,9,Fceremony at the Big Pit National Coal
OL,10,FMuseum.
OL,12,FThe Disused Mine and Quarry Tips
OL,13,F(Wales) Bill was passed by the Senedd
OL,14,Fin July.
OL,16,FIt aims to better coordinate the
OL,17,Fmanagement of disused tips across the
OL,18,Fcountry and improve public safety.
