OL,3,CDisused coal tips safety bill becomes
OL,4,Claw in Wales
OL,6,FThere has been considerable scrutiny
OL,7,Fof Wales' coal mining legacy since the
OL,8,Fcollapse of a coal tip near Tylorstown
OL,9,Fin February 2020.
OL,11,FA further slip in Cwmtillery in
OL,12,FNovember 2024 caused homes to be
OL,13,Fevacuated.
OL,15,FThere are 2573 recorded coal tips in
OL,16,FWales.
OL,18,F360 are in the highest categories of
OL,19,Frisk - Category C and D - and are
OL,20,Fclassed as those with the potential to
OL,21,Fimpact public safety.
