OL,3,CDisused coal tips safety bill becomes
OL,4,Claw in Wales
OL,6,FThe First Minister says establishing
OL,7,Fthe new Disused Tips Authority in
OL,8,FApril 2027 will formalise the
OL,9,Finspection work being carried out.
OL,11,F"We've changed the law, and we are
OL,12,Fgoing even further by setting up a new
OL,13,Forganisation to carry on this
OL,14,Fimportant safety work for generations
OL,15,Fto come" she said.
